name: aarivan/Matching-Algorithms-for-the-Adwords-Problem
description: Problem: We are given a set of advertisers each of whom have a daily budget Bi . When a user performs a query, an ad request is placed online and a group of advertisers can then bid for that advertisement slot. The bid of advertiser i for ad request q is denoted as bi q. We assume that the bids are small with respect to the daily budgets of the advertisers (i.e, for each i and q, b iq << Bi ) . Moreover, each advertisement slot can be allocated to at most one advertiser and the advertiser is charged his bid from his budget. The objective is to maximize the amount of money received from the advertisers
